"You have given a field of view of %.2f degrees.\n"
" But the orthographic projection is limited to a field of view of 180 "
"degress.\n"
"Do you want still use that high value?"
msgstr ""
"Es wurde ein Bildwinkel von %.2f Grad eingegeben.\n"
